### ============================================================
### EVENTS API REQUESTS
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000/v1
### ============================================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================================
### PUBLIC ROUTES (No Authentication Required)
### ============================================================

### Get all events
GET {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

### With pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/events?page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "message": "Events fetched successfully",
#     "data": {
#         "events": [
#             {
#                 "id": 1,
#                 "title": "Community Town Hall Meeting",
#                 "slug": "community-town-hall-meeting",
#                 "description": "Join us for our monthly town hall...",
#                 "image": "https://example.com/event1.jpg",
#                 "location": "Community Center, Main Street",
#                 "event_date": "2025-01-15",
#                 "start_time": "10:00:00",
#                 "end_time": "12:00:00",
#                 "status": "upcoming"
#             }
#         ],
#         "pagination": {...}
#     }
# }

###

### Get upcoming events
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/upcoming
Content-Type: application/json

### With limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/upcoming?limit=5
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get single event by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/community-town-hall-meeting
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### ADMIN ROUTES (Requires web_admin role)
### ============================================================

### Get all events (including past)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get single event by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/events/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Create new event
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "title": "Health Screening Day",
    "description": "Free health screening for all community members. Blood pressure, diabetes, and eye tests available.",
    "image": "https://example.com/health-day.jpg",
    "location": "District Hospital, Healthcare Road",
    "event_date": "2025-02-10",
    "start_time": "08:00",
    "end_time": "16:00",
    "registration_required": true,
    "max_attendees": 200,
    "status": "upcoming"
}

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "message": "Event created successfully",
#     "data": {
#         "event": {
#             "id": 2,
#             "title": "Health Screening Day",
#             "slug": "health-screening-day",
#             ...
#         }
#     }
# }

###

### Update event
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/events/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "title": "Updated Event Title",
    "location": "New Venue, New Street",
    "start_time": "09:00"
}

###

### Delete event
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/events/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###
